===美利坚帝国及其挑战者===
[[File:American_empire.PNG|thumb]]领土及其武装干涉地区，在图中用深蓝色标出]]

{{main|美利坚帝国}}

由于[[二战|二战]]以后，特别是近几十年来[[美国|美国]]的迅速崛起和在全世界的[[霸权主义|霸权主义]]活动，美国也被认为是一个全球帝国，被称为“[[美利坚帝国|美利坚帝国]]”，也有人认为它和古代的[[罗马帝国|罗马帝国]]类似，所以又称之为“[[新罗马帝国|新罗马帝国]]”。不管美国自己愿不愿意承认自己是一个帝国或者是[[帝国主义|帝国主义]]国家，但不可否认的是，美国是当今世界上唯一的[[超级大国|超级大国]]，它在全球的[[经济|经济]]、[[政治|政治]]、[[军事|军事]]、[[文化|文化]]等众多领域的巨大优势和强大影响力都是他国无法比拟的<ref>[http://www.britannica.com/ebi/article-230262 大英百科] {{Wayback|url=http://www.britannica.com/ebi/article-230262 |date=20070505063957 }} ''世界上唯一的超级强国''</ref><ref>[http://www.iht.com/articles/1999/02/05/france.t_0.php "To Paris, U.S. Looks Like a 'Hyperpower'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iht.com/articles/1999/02/05/france.t_0.php |date=20051027111515 }}, ''The International Herald Tribune''</ref><ref>无论是以[[各国国内生产总值列表_(购买力平价)|购买力平价]]或是[[各国国内生产总值列表_(国际汇率)|国际汇率]]计算，美国都有着世界上最高的[[国内生产总值|GDP]]、最高的军事预算，所有数据可以在 [https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/rankorder/2001rank.html 这里] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/rankorder/2001rank.html |date=20070411165203 }} 和 [https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/rankorder/2067rank.html 这里] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/rankorder/2067rank.html |date=20070510033139 }} 找到。</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.foreignaffairs.org/20040701faessay83406/eliot-a-cohen/history-and-the-hyperpower.html |title=History and the Hyperpower |publisher=Foreign Affairs |accessdate=2006-09-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060825044410/http://www.foreignaffairs.org/20040701faessay83406/eliot-a-cohen/history-and-the-hyperpower.html |archivedate=2006-08-25 }}</ref><ref>Alfredo Valladão, ''Democratic Hegemony and American Hegemony'', Cambridge Review of International Affairs, 2006.</ref><ref>{{cite web | url= http://news.xinhuanet.com/ziliao/2002-01/28/content_257426.htm | title= 美利坚合众国概况（美国概况） | publisher= 新华网 | accessdate= 2006-09-03 | archive-date= 2006-09-01 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20060901033649/http://news.xinhuanet.com/ziliao/2002-01/28/content_257426.htm | dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>Robert S. Litwak, ''[http://wwics.si.edu/topics/pubs/imperial.pdf The Imperial Republic After 9/11] {{Wayback|url=http://wwics.si.edu/topics/pubs/imperial.pdf |date=20051213214310 }}, The Wilson Quarterly, 2006-09-03资料'',</ref><ref>Van Ness, Peter, ''Hegemony, not anarchy: why China and Japan are not balancing US unipolar power.''(2001), Technical Report Working papers 2001/4, Department of International Relations, RSPAS, ANU.</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nwc.navy.mil/press/Review/2002/spring/art1-sp2.htm | title=AMERICAN PRIMACY | publisher=Naval War College Review | accessdate=2006-09-03 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060905153532/http://www.nwc.navy.mil/press/Review/2002/spring/art1-sp2.htm | archivedate=2006-09-05 }}</ref><ref>Francis McCollum Feeley, ''[http://dimension.ucsd.edu/~flonidier/publications/Students/Imperialism.pdf Université Stendhal Grenoble 3 DEA Etudes Anglophones] {{Wayback|url=http://dimension.ucsd.edu/~flonidier/publications/Students/Imperialism.pdf |date=20050328102709 }}'', pp. 11-12, dimension.ucsd.edu</ref><ref>Stephen M. Walt, ''[http://www.comw.org/pda/swalt.pdf The Ties That Fray: WhyEurope and America Are Drifting Apart] {{Wayback|url=http://www.comw.org/pda/swalt.pdf |date=20070411003051 }}'', TheNational Interest, no. 54 (Winter 1998/99), pp. 3.</ref>，在全世界可以说是没有对手。

然而也有人认为美国并非完全没有对手，[[中國|中國]]、[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]、[[欧盟|欧盟]]、[[印度|印度]]等都是美国的潜在对手。

{{-}}

